[normal]1.3 
[normal]While the 
[normal]c
[normal]all for evidence focusses solely on bus, rail and car, 
[normal]Flybe believes there is an important role for 
[normal]aviat
[normal]ion in providing reliable 
[normal]and frequent transport services for 
[normal]isolated
[normal] communities
[normal].
[normal] This response aims to briefly outline the importance of air services for those communities and is something 
